erve-partners-with-vista-equity-partners-for-new-strategic-investment-to-fuel-next-phase-of-growth-300483890.html |title=Upserve Partners with Vista Equity Partners for New Strategic Investment to Fuel Next Phase of Growth |website=PR Newswire |date=2017-07-06 |accessdate=2019-09-08}}</ref>\n|-\n| August 2017\n| Vista acquired [[Framingham]]-based software company [[Applause (software company)|Applause]].<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/boston/news/2017/08/23/private-equity-firm-to-buy-goldman-backed-applause.html|title=Private equity firm to buy Goldman-backed Applause, with IPO still a possibility|date=August 23, 2017|website=bizjournals|access-date=2019-12-06}}</ref>\n|-\n| November 2017\n| Vista announced they were acquiring a majority stake in [[Jamf]], a provider of Apple device management software based in [[Minneapolis]], [[Minnesota]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.startribune.com/vista-equity-buys-controlling-stake-in-mpls-tech-firm-jamf/450465263 |title=Vista Equity buys controlling stake in Mpls. tech firm Jamf |website=StarTribune.com |date=2017-12-17 |accessdate=2019-07-11}}</ref> Jamf has since acquired Orchard & Grove and Zuludesk.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.appleworld.today/blog/2019/2/5/jamf-acquires-zuludesk-an-apple-education-tech-solution |title=Jamf acquires ZuluDesk, an Apple education tech solution |website=appleworld.today |date=2019-02-05 |accessdate=2019-07-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| November 2017\n| Vista completed its acquisition of NAVEX Global, a global SaaS-based ethics and compliance software and content provider <ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/silicon-forest/index.ssf/2014/12/secrets_of_navex_global_sale_e.html|title=Secrets of NAVEX Global sale emerging -- it was among the biggest deals for an Oregon company in a decade|website=Oregonlive.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/vista-equity-partners-emerges-from-private-equity-shadows-1413338405|title=Vista Equity Partners Emerges From Private-Equity Shadows|first=Gillian|last=Tan|date=15 October 2014|publisher=|via=www.wsj.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2014/10/15/term-sheet-wednesday-october-15/|title=Term Sheet -- Wednesday, October 15|website=Fortune.com}}</ref><ref name=\"auto\"/>\n|-\n|December 2018\n|Vista announced they entered into a definitive agreement to acquire MINDBODY, the leading technology platform for the fitness, beauty and wellness services industries, for $1.9 billion.Under the terms of the agreement, Vista will acquire all outstanding shares of MINDBODY common stock and  MINDBODY shareholders will receive $36.50 in cash per share, representing a 68% premium to the unaffected closing price as of December 21, 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mindbodyonline.com/company/press/mindbody-enters-into-definitive-agreement-to-be-acquired-by-vista-equity-partners-for|title=MINDBODY Enters into Definitive Agreement to be Acquired by Vista Equity Partners for $1.9 Billion|date=2018-12-24|website=Mindbodyonline.com|access-date=2018-12-28}}</ref> \n|-\n|November 2018\n|Vista announced the acquisition of Apptio for $1.94 billion, paying $38 per share. Apptio develops cloud-based business management software.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/vista-nears-deal-to-buy-software-firm-apptio-for-1-9-billion-1541988001|title=Vista Reaches Deal to Buy Software Firm Apptio for $1.94 Billion|last=Cooper|first=Laura|date=2018-11-11|newspaper=[[The Wall Street Journal]]|access-date=2019-01-08}}</ref> \nVista took a majority share in Wrike, a project management software company.\n|-\n|February 2019\n|Vista announced a strategic partnership with Four Winds Interactive, a provider for enterprise-grade visual communications.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2019/02/05/1710333/0/en/Four-Winds-Interactive-Announces-Strategic-Partnership-with-Vista-Equity-Partners.html|title=Four Winds Interactive Announces Strategic Partnership with 